{"type":"message","id":"6859cf05","parentId":"4963ce5a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:49:50.687Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the Session Startup sequence as instructed. I need to read the required files before responding. Let me check what's required:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md - already loaded in Project Context\n2. Read USER.md - already loaded in Project Context\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) - today is 2026-03-24, yesterday is 2026-03-23\n4. If in MAIN SESSION, also read MEMORY.md\n\nThe files SOUL.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, IDENTITY.md, AGENTS.md, HEARTBEAT.md, BOOTSTRAP.md are already in the Project Context. But I need to check the memory files and MEMORY.md.\n\n\nI can see BOOTSTRAP.md still exists, which means I haven't completed the bootstrap sequence yet. I need to work through the memory files for today and yesterday to get caught up on recent context. Once I have that information, I can delete BOOTSTRAP.md and establish my identity.","thinkingSignature":"807ba7b6af58438061c88997028711523c218e2f989cb67a8efece4a6bf2f52c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_osldoi8q6ewo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ 2>/dev/null && cat /home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"No MEMORY.md found\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":287,"cacheRead":9704,"cacheWrite":8880,"totalTokens":18961,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.00034439999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00029111999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.0010655999999999999,"total":0.0017281199999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774345774523}}
